727012f-a.title: Queens: Jamaica Avenue - 125th Street
727012f-a.text:
Jamaica Ave. (elevated structure thereon), east from 125th to
126th Streets, showing in the background at the corner the P. Opper
Hotel of 1891. It was demolished in March 1926.
April 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
